I think what you want here is:
```diff
-        const fs::path asmap_path = GetDataDir() / gArgs.GetArg("-asmap", DEFAULT_ASMAP_FILENAME);
+        std::string asmap_file = gArgs.GetArg("-asmap", "");
+        if (asmap_file.empty()) {
+            asmap_file = DEFAULT_ASMAP_FILENAME;
+        }
+        const fs::path asmap_path = GetDataDir() / asmap_file;
```
This provides the behavior of defaulting to `DEFAULT_ASMAP_FILENAME` if the user passes `-asmap` without a filename.

