@pinheadmz added a ``critical_as`` field to a getpeerinfo RPC call response. I had to do some refactoring for this.

I couldn't find a good way to test it with functional or unit tests really, because it's hard to avoid triggering ``GetNetClass() == NET_UNROUTABLE/NET_LOCAL``. And triggering this prevents returning an asmap. I'd be glad if someone suggests a good way to test it.
I tested this behavior by running a node.

